Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:20.80,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}哼唱的旋律 勾起无尽的思绪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.80,0:00:24.69,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尘封的记忆 闪耀刺眼的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:28.62,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta remember　现在的你仍握有梦的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.62,0:00:32.82,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那时一样 绽放光芒吧 少年的情怀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:34.82,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在栏杆上刻下将来的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:36.96,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时起我经历了多少沧桑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.96,0:00:38.87,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在现实与理想的夹缝中摇摆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:41.09,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热情的火焰也已燃烧殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.09,0:00:42.87,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等! 我说等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.87,0:00:45.08,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺起胸膛 胜负才刚刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.08,0:00:47.13,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃的时候就是游戏结束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:49.28,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的双手打破现状吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:50.07,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:53.30,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们曾为了一线希望而全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.30,0:00:55.24,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了明天而努力生存
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.24,0:00:57.30,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的心情已经忘记了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:00:58.98,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春没有极限
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:01.99,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇心和年龄无关 我是这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.99,0:01:03.12,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:05.60,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We wanna make the fream come true　所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:09.53,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绽放吧 绽放吧 绽放吧 热情之花绽放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.53,0:01:12.73,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绽放吧 绽放吧 绽放吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.73,0:01:17.57,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼唱的旋律勾起无尽的思绪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.57,0:01:21.73,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尘封的记忆闪耀刺眼的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.73,0:01:25.57,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta remember　现在的你仍握有梦的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.57,0:01:30.47,OpeningCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}就像那时一样 绽放光芒吧少年的情怀
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.37,0:22:25.77,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}想要真心喜欢上一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.77,0:22:29.82,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却在害怕内心受到伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.82,0:22:33.93,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明自己什么也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.93,0:22:37.17,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却只是说出逞强的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.17,0:22:45.19,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏于内心的软弱 我视而不见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.19,0:22:50.23,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连那种事情 也能轻易驱散的巨大的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:54.26,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于找到了　You are my sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.26,0:22:58.37,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fly away Fly away　如果和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.37,0:23:02.47,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fly away Fly away　就不会感到害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.47,0:23:06.33,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fly away Fly away　即使失败也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.33,0:23:10.21,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go another place　Take it easy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.21,0:23:14.47,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fly away Fly away　让我飞上蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.47,0:23:18.66,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fly away Fly away　不再感到迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:22.55,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fly away Fly away　这都是因为有你在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.55,0:23:28.41,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1500)}Take my chance　Believe in myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.29,0:23:45.02,EndingCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Take it easy
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反射膜修得怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光粒子泉干涸的状态下 修理进展很慢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.70,0:01:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们到底要在这儿窝到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的混着沙子的饭菜我已经吃腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.50,0:01:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去恐怕要花上一年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去联系一下反射膜职人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.00,0:02:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不是和军队有关系么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能暗地里给我们做么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么哈普恐怕又要愁眉苦脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 一共需要几张反射膜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少276张
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么多 那得多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概要…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别算了 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单来说我们现在没钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.40,0:02:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为月光号不能飞 所以没法接活儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不干活儿但谁也没少吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之钱是单方面减少
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但总也不能就这么在这儿等着它自己长好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当成是先期投资
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:02:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时取消化妆品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月光号现在进入第5战斗配置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说进入缺钱模式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Skyrock Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮你拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许你碰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之别靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优莱卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我头疼 今天就让我休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么 优莱卡身体不好 你来驾驶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:03:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向来小心的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优莱卡是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩出什么事了么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为你们是纯洁的一对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说大声点 风声很吵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道为什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是知道我就不用犯愁了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩的心就像秋天的天空啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是秋天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 这是老话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好险 小心点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是接近过科拉利安么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就从那之前开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有点偏离轨道 优莱卡和我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之前一直很好么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是吧 总之还挺投缘的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春真是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么样 推倒了么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那接吻总有过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 连这都没有么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人要主动进攻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈普 通信器一直开着么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是么 哎呀 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰顿 男人就是要进攻进攻再进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话让只会跟在希尔德\N屁股后面转的人说出来可没什么说服力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那叫男人的包容心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓包容心就是成天跟人认错道歉么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之一句话 女孩的心就像秋天的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这刚才听你说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人别为小事斤斤计较
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得 咱们一起也这么长时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是对于你 对于你的心情 我却一点都不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想更多地了解你 因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 抱歉 光顾着睡 有事么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希尔德找你 叫你帮忙洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 接下来该叠衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 看好 袜子要像这样折成三叠 然后张开 这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 嗯 这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我自己来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近你是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:08:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你竟然自己不去开尼尔瓦修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不想开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为尼尔瓦修心情不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果兰顿不在 我就开不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得呢 把尼尔瓦修看成你的女朋友倒是很合适
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经和自己很要好的女孩找到了男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎的跟这个女孩总会闹点别扭不是么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得好像自己的朋友被那男朋友抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在吃醋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃醋?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这种表情 就像从来没有过似的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候真是搞不懂你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你还是应该好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是在吃谁的醋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是尼尔瓦修呢还是兰顿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叠好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也叠好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算这样呆到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候? 你不喜欢跟我独处么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知我问的不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是存心逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是无可奈何吧 月光号现在这副样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么办 修好以后怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修好以后你又准备逃到哪儿去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.20,0:09:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是挖掘业者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:10:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信这里还有矿脉 认为这里的某处一定埋藏着梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好悲伤的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃德蒙德在么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.50,0:10:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃德蒙德不在么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经停业了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃德蒙德 是我 肯戈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃德蒙德死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然一大早就喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喝酒花的是自己的钱 你有意见么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.20,0:11:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止吧 尼尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 你知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 你们是讨债的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要反射膜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说我们是来买反射膜的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为你要说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那东西我已经不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又费事又没销路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就是来订货的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.40,0:11:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了我不做这种狗屁活儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.80,0:11:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊 莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没出息 这是埃德蒙德的儿子该说的话么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:12:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙可是在制作反射膜上倾注了全部的热情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可结果怎么样 一贫如洗 结果患上了绝望病死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝望病…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱我们有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 还没还价啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工人们都跑光了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.30,0:12:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是来收货的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过机器已经很久没用过了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怕么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这什么意思 我再怎么喝酒这手艺可是没落下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让我们见识见识你这手艺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成交
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:13:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 喝点酒才好干活儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝成这样不要紧么 当初我确实这么想过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见了 奥拉德彭特山谷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是有一点点光粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要去飞鱼聚集的场所吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是等它们聚集 是我们想办法让它们聚集
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有音乐好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 就只有这种啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着这种音乐我就想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就喝酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝酒会好些么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少你就搞不清弄得你想吐的是音乐还是酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死 喝就喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 再多喝点 再多喝点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给蒙多吉那小子喝了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌龙茶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.00,0:14:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌龙茶?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人们开始喝酒狂欢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照尼尔的说法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:15:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞鱼会飞到魂魄驱动器边上的快乐的人身边来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真是这样么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喝得还不够多 这点程度的话飞鱼会飞走的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来表演我的第36种绝活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饺子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 再多喝点 热烈点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉纯粹是在胡来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么没什么啊 你最近状态不好不是么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也很担心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们好像在躲着我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是自然的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.20,0:16:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也不会接近闷闷不乐的人的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微笑微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喝啊喝啊 怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要多想快乐的事就好了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:16:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别停下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 大家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别胡说 好戏这才要开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 用滑空板压住它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆在那儿别动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别发呆 小心后面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:17:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:17:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰顿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰顿!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先捉一只
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样 我们努力收集了不少飞鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样搬到工作室去就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不过接下去就是我一个人的活儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人很辛苦的吧 我们也帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专家的工作用不着外行插手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是想帮忙的话 就处理下那宴会的残局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专家的工作么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这让我想起了爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼尔也是个职人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当晚 尼尔的工作室的灯光一直没有熄灭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除去转去地方军的7人 全员到齐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很感谢你们一直以来的暗中支持
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们等这一天很久了 中校…不 听说您晋升上校了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是个虚名 无聊陈腐的老规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前几天的预算委员会 正式批准了部队的重组
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前虽然只有上校和我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但相信几天之内各位就会接到转属命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:19:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊 无聊透顶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤人会议至今仍不了解其真意么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是给出这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就足够让那些半吊子的学者折腾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们存在的社会就是如此浅薄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.50,0:20:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,始终坚定不移地相信自己就是正义的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都该去死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要揭穿这社会的虚伪 掌握世界的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人类再次以主人的身份君临这星球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成英雄阿德洛克·萨斯顿的未竟事业
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 就是第二次爱之夏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.80,0:20:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 最后的一批也固定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:20:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.10,0:20:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃德蒙德也会为你骄傲的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸要是还在的话 这会儿一定会踹我的屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.90,0:21:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 总算最后做了一次漂亮活儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要关门了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.30,0:21:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别误会 要是能继续我也想继续 可是没生意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队不是你的主顾么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年开始忽然不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下就能修理了 快搬进去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过一想到是用飞鱼做的 就总觉得有点可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:22:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…不过 很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.30,0:22:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候 我觉得和优莱卡的关系似乎有所恢复了
